        <br><br>
        Include:<br>
        Masa de pranz va  fi bufet deschis și este inclusa .<br>
        Băuturi non alocolice ,fructe și dulciuri orientale.<br>
        Echipament de snorkeling.<br>
        <br><br>
        Pret:<br>
        50 € - 60 € variaza in functie de numarul de persoane<br>
        De preferat grup de  intre 8 si 11 persoane
        <br><br>
        Cand:<br>
        intreaba ghidul
    </p>
    <p id="paragraph-usa" class="paragraph invisible">
        A day trip with snorkeling to the turtles in Abu Dabbab, with our El Majico team.
        Departure will be around 6:00 depending on the hotel and we will arrive around 9:00. We will swim with the turtles and we will see brightly colored corals and fish. Turtles in their natural habitat.
        <br><br>
        Include:<br>
        Lunch will be open buffet and is included.<br>
        Non-alcoholic beverages, fruits and oriental sweets.<br>
        Snorkeling equipment.<br>
        <br><br>
        Price:<br>
        € 50 - € 60 varies depending on the number of people.<br>
        Preferably a group of between 8 and 11 people.
        <br><br>
        When:<br>
        asks the guide
    </p>
</body>
<script>
    const translateBtnUsa = document.getElementById("translation-btn-usa")
    const translateBtnRo = document.getElementById("translation-btn-ro")
    const paragraphUsa = document.getElementById("paragraph-usa")
    const paragraphRo = document.getElementById("paragraph-ro")

    translateBtnUsa.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.remove("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.add("invisible")
    })

    translateBtnRo.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.add("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.remove("invisible")
    })

</script>
